## 📌 How to Use

1. Copy the prompt above.
2. Replace all placeholder values with your own information.
3. Paste the prompt into Claude AI.
4. Copy the generated Markdown.
5. Create a repository with the same name as your GitHub username.
6. Paste the Markdown into `README.md`.

---

## 💡 Pro Tips

- Include only your strongest projects.
- Keep your bio concise.
- Update the README regularly.
- Add a portfolio and resume link.
- Use high-quality badges and stats.

